# Whoop Developer API — get from developer.whoop.com
# 1. Sign in with your Whoop account
# 2. Create app named "Baseline"
# 3. Set redirect URI to: https://<your-netlify-subdomain>.netlify.app/api/whoop-callback
# 4. Copy Client ID and Client Secret below
